<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171277>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Odonteus gandhara n. sp.: head and pronotum of male in dorsal (1 a) and lateral view (1 b); head and pronotum of female (4). O. armiger (Scopoli) (Southern Moravia: Hustopece): head and pronotum of male in dorsal (2 a) and lateral view (2 b); head and pronotum of female (3)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171277/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171278>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 6. Aedeagus of Odonteus gandhara n. sp. (5) and O. armiger (Scopoli) (Southern Moravia: Hustopece) (6): dorsal view (a) and lateral view (b)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171278/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

